Luvdisc live in shallow seas in the tropics. This heart-shaped
Pokmon earned its name by swimming after loving couples it
spotted in the oceans waves.

Le corps en forme de cur de Lovdisc reprsente lamour
et les sentiments. On raconte quun couple qui rencontre
ce Pokmon saimera jusqu la fin des temps.

Liebiskus herzfrmiger Krper ist ein Symbol der Liebe

Luvdisc tiene forma de corazn y simboliza el amor y el

Il corpo a forma di cuore di Luvdisc  il simbolo delle storie

destinate a vivere unintensa passione che non avr mai fine.

Luvdiscs heart-shaped body is a symbol of love and romance.

Un Lovdisc esseul perd tout entrain et baisse
sa garde. Le Bekipan nattend que cela pour
frapper.

Einsame Liebiskus verlieren den Lebensmut und
vernachlssigen die Deckung. Diese Schwche
nutzen Pelipper, um sie sich zu schnappen.

Cuando un Luvdisc se halla solo, su energa

aprovechan los Pelipper para hacerse con ellos.

Se rimane solo, Luvdisc perde vitalit
e abbassa la guardia, diventando una facile
preda per Pelipper.

If a Luvdisc is left on its own, it becomes
despondent, leaving itself open to attack.
That is when Pelipper snatch them up.

Comme il est trs populaire auprs des

Es popular entre las parejas de enamorados,

molto popolare tra gli innamorati, perci viene

Loving couples have a soft spot for this

In passato  stato vittima di una caccia sfrenata

There was an era when it was overfished due to
